description:
If you need an experienced personal injury attorney in Raritan, New Jersey, do not hesitate to contact Levinson Axelrod, P.A., for a free consultation. With 75 years of experience, our firm is prepared to handle the full range of personal injury cases from car accidents to work accidents to wrongful death. Contact our firm today.

We offer 100 percent FREE case evaluations to help determine if you have sufficient grounds to file a lawsuit, and we only get paid if we win your case.

If you or a loved one was injured in an accident caused by the negligence of another person or corporate entity, you may be entitled to recover monetary damages for your injuries. Typically, Levinson Axelrod, P.A., will aggressively pursue compensation for lost wages, medical bills, property damage, and pain and suffering. We understand the financial peril that can result from a serious accident, and we will fight for the maximum monetary compensation you are owed in your specific situation.

Celebrating 75 years of practice.

With the extensive experience of our New Jersey personal injury lawyers and the diverse backgrounds of our staff of dedicated professionals, Levinson Axelrod, P.A., is prepared to represent clients throughout the state. We are equipped to handle even the most challenging cases involving complex injuries. When necessary, we can call upon trusted experts in various fields to lend their knowledge and insight to your case. Trust us to diligently fight for you every step of the legal process.

Contact our law firm to schedule a free consultation and receive an honest case evaluation. We maintain seven area offices for the convenience of our clients.
